quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  39,75,"Yi'oyaa Malaa'ikaen, he…ďe taarii Arsi kin, he…ďe cubbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Goonga √Īaawiree hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Wi'ee on tuma: "Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo tagoore"."
  40,1,"Haa, miim."
  40,2,"Jippagol deftere nde, ko immorde e Allah, pool…óo, ganndo oon."
  40,3,"Kaforoowo bakkatuuji …óin, Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuyee, ca…ótu…óo lepte, Joom yaajeende. Dewetee…óo alaa, si wonaa kaŇčko. Ko ka makko woni ruttorde nden."
  40,4,"Alaa ko wee√Īdata e aayeeje Allah …óen, si wonaa yeddu…ďe …ďen. Wota a hoditor ko …ďe dillirta kon ka leydi."
  40,5,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďeen e pe…óle …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, yedduno (Nulaa…ďe mum …ďeen), mofte kala himmiri nanngugol Nulaa…óo mun oon. ∆Āe njeddiri meere, fii no bonnitira (goonga) kan. Kono Min nanngi …ďe. Taskii no nanngal am ngal wa…ótinirnoo !"
  40,6,"Ko wano nii Konngol Joomi maa ngol, jojjiri e yeddu…ďe …ďeen : "Won'de pellet, ko …ďe yim…ďe Yiite"."
  40,7,"∆Āeen (Malaa'ikaa…ďe) roondii…ďe Arsiki kin, e won…ďe bannge makki …ďen, hi…ďe cubbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ngooŇč…óina mo, …ďe insinorana gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen (wiide): "Joomi amen, A ya√Ī√Īirii kala hu'unde, yurmeende e ganndal. Yawtan …ďen tuubu…ďe, …ďe njokki laawol Maa ngol, da…óndaa …ďe kadi lepte Dul…ďoowe ngeen."